11 An Act relating to retirement; amending 74 O.S. 2021,
Section 920, which relates to the Oklahoma Public
12 Employees Retirement System; modifying employer
contribution amount for certain time frame; providing
13 an effective date; and declaring an emergency.
14
15
16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 920, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 920. (1) Effective July 1, 1994, every state agency
20 which is a participating employer shall contribute to the System an
21 amount equal to eleven and one-half percent (11 1/2%) of the monthly
22 compensation of each member, but not in excess of Forty Thousand
23 Dollars ($40,000.00).
24
